    <!-- C03 M02 -->
    <div class="modal" id="modal10">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">PLANTING & MANUARING
                <button class="icon modal-close">
                    <i class="material-icons">close</i>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-body">Planting:<br> For planting rainy season is the best, planting is done at beginning of monsoon in dry region and at the end
            of the monsoon in high rainfall area. Planting is done either in flat beds or in shallow trenches. The planting distance
            in the single row system should be 25 x 60 x 90 cm and in double row system 25 x 30 x 90cm.<br><br>
            
            Manuring: <br>Pineapple is heavy feeder. It requires 600 kg N, 400 kg P and 400kg K per ha. Nitrogen is given in two split
            doses, first at begining of monsoon and second in the month of February..</div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button class="link modal-close">Close</button>
            </div>
