                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">Harvesting and Yield: <br>It matures in both 15 to 20 months after planting. Usually flowering takes place from February to
            April and fruits are ready from July to September. The fruits are harvested when they just become yellow. An average
            yield is 10 to15 tonnes per hectare.</div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button class="link modal-close">Close</button>
            </div>
